body_html:
You can get the .so and .jar files that are required to build the apps from http://ci.tensorflow.org/view/Nightly/job/nightly-android/

  1. Click on the Last stable build
  2. Artifact
  3. Download all files in the zip, then you are ready with .so and .jar, place them in the correct places and you are done.

body:
You can get the .so and .jar files that are required to build the apps from http://ci.tensorflow.org/view/Nightly/job/nightly-android/
1. Click on the Last stable build
2. Artifact
3. Download all files in the zip, then you are ready with .so and .jar, place them in the correct places and you are done.
